headline: Agilent Research Catalyst Award Presented to Columbia University for Professor Pawel Muranski
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., March 19, 2025--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced that Columbia University has received an Agilent Research Catalyst (ARC) Award on behalf of Dr. Pawel Muranski, an internationally recognized researcher and physician-scientist specializing in bone marrow transplant (BMT) and cancer cellular immunotherapy.
